  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This package encodes a credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. The underlying model has been applied in clinical research contexts to support ventricular assist device design decisions at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are addressed; seven were formally assessed and six were flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. Despite gaps, a conditional acceptance was recorded following expert panel review. No structured Context of Use object is bound to this unit; the intended-use scope is conveyed only through the narrative description above.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-experimental-hemolysis",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-cfd-outputs-montecarlo"
  ],
